Package: blizz
Title: R interface to Blizzards API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Tyler",
           family = "Littlefield",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "tylurp1@gmail.com")
Description: The goal of blizz is to give R users an interface to explore
    Blizzards developer API. Generally speaking, R is a great tool for 
    interactive work and this package is meant to make Blizzard data exploration
    easy and enjoyable.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
